βάρος / baros / bar'-os
=== Etymology ===

Probably from the same as [[βάσις]] {{GG|939}} (through the notion of going down; compare [[βάθος ]] {{GG|899}}); 
=== Noun ===
[[weight]]; in the New Testament only, figuratively a load, abundance, authority: - [[burden]] (-some), weight.

